| **Updates** | Updates and modifications by Authorized Contributors; copyright in Updates belongs to the relevant Contributor, subject to a right of first refusal for the Author or Successor ([CONTRIBUTOR_LICENSE.md](legal.en/CONTRIBUTOR_LICENSE.md) § 6; see also [legal.ru/CONTRIBUTOR_LICENSE.md](legal.ru/CONTRIBUTOR_LICENSE.md)) |
